Real production setup always:

Code (main.tf)   → Git repository (GitHub/GitLab/CodeCommit)
State file       → S3 backend
Lock file        → DynamoDB

Three separate places
All safe ✅

# When you clone and run terraform init
git clone your-repo
cd your-repo
terraform init
